	(12,1,'2017-04-22 09:08:10','2017-04-22 13:08:10','Classic. Probably timeless.','Taxi Driver','','publish','closed','closed','','taxi-driver','','','2017-05-24 09:21:22','2017-05-24 13:21:22','',0,'http://ethans-macbook-air.local/mymovies/?post_type=movie&#038;p=12',0,'movie','',0),
	(13,1,'2016-12-25 09:11:35','2016-12-25 14:11:35','Loved this movie. Probably because it\'s <em>not</em> your typical Star Wars story.\r\n\r\nThere\'s a great line: \"There are no Jedi here! Only dreamers like this fool.\" I think that sums up the feel of the movie. These characters are not Jedi. They exist in a world abandoned by the Jedi. They are making do, struggling to survive, without the Jedi.\r\n\r\nThat makes the story less fanciful, more believable and possibly more relatable.\r\n\r\nThe ending, without giving it away, is also not a typical Star Wars ending.\r\n\r\nAlso, K-2SO is my spirit animal.','Star Wars: Rogue One','','publish','closed','closed','','star-wars-rogue-one','','','2017-05-24 09:17:24','2017-05-24 13:17:24','',0,'http://ethans-macbook-air.local/mymovies/?post_type=movie&#038;p=13',0,'movie','',0),
	(14,1,'2017-04-23 09:19:19','2017-04-23 13:19:19','Long but could have been longer. Brutal, emotional. Did not like the ending.','Silence','','publish','closed','closed','','silence','','','2017-05-24 09:21:08','2017-05-24 13:21:08','',0,'http://ethans-macbook-air.local/mymovies/?post_type=movie&#038;p=14',0,'movie','',0);
